Package Lab4

Class IntNode

java.lang.Object
Lab4.IntNode
public class IntNode extends Object
IntNode is a collection of int numbers. IntNode is a linked list collection. The last node in a list will have a null link.

      public static IntNode listSort(IntNode head)
